The SGE template provides:
- **Authentication System** - Ready-to-use auth with Supabase
- **Database Schema** - Core tables for user management
- **UI Components** - Tailwind + shadcn/ui component library
- **Mobile Support** - Capacitor integration for native apps
- **Deployment** - Vercel deployment configuration

